    "classroomUse": "<strong>For Teachers:</strong> Give students a roleplay prompt: \"You just moved from a hot, quiet village to a cold, noisy city.\" Have them write three sentences: 1. What they <em>used to</em> do in the village. 2. What they <em>are getting used to</em> in the city. 3. What they hope they <em>will be used to</em> next year.",
