    "classroomUse": "<strong>For Teachers:</strong> Do a \"Timeline Stand-Up.\" Have one student sit in a chair marked \"Past\" and one in a chair marked \"Present.\" Point to a subject on the board (\"The dogs\"). The Present student shouts \"ARE!\" and the Past student shouts \"WERE!\" Fast-paced repetition builds the reflex.",
