    "meaning": "- <strong>There is / There was:</strong> Used when the true subject (the thing that exists) is <strong>Singular</strong> or <strong>Uncountable</strong>.<br>- <strong>There are / There were:</strong> Used when the true subject is <strong>Plural</strong>.",
