        "wrong": "'Rina and Sari is friends.'",
        "correct": "",
        "explanation": "Mistake: 'Rina and Sari is friends.' | Solution: 'and' makes them plural. Say 'Rina and Sari are friends.'",
        "fix": "'and' makes them plural. Say 'Rina and Sari are friends.'"
